summary: To achieve professional excellence in development sector through devotion, hard work with sheer determination & commitment. I am a passionate Environmentalist currently pursuing my Masters from University of Dhaka. I have done my Graduation (BURP) from Khulna University of Engineering and Technology . My area of interest are Climate change, Sustainable development, Water Resource Management, Land-use planning, youth development, human rights etc. I am looking forward to engage myself in project managerial positions.
